      "bookmarkId": "3300046359_51_6490-6565",
      "chapterUid": 51,
      "range": "6490-6565",
      "markText": "期望不对等的忠诚，这种观念全无实际意义，无非是想取悦世袭体系里的老大罢了。夫妻关系里，我觉得善意和体贴才是最重要的，而性的不忠未必会导致这种关系终结。",
      "totalCount": 13920,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046359&chapterUid=51&rangeStart=6490&rangeEnd=6565",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/43332d10813ab789bg0191c4?chapterUid=51&rangeStart=6490&rangeEnd=6565"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046359_50_4878-4950",
      "chapterUid": 50,
      "range": "4878-4950",
      "markText": "她谈论绘画时感觉非常棒，这下我恍然明白，为什么从她身上我看不到空虚之感。她是那种拥有最大幸运的典型例子，不管经历了怎样的苦难，却天生能成就事业。",
      "totalCount": 10670,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046359&chapterUid=50&rangeStart=4878&rangeEnd=4950",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/43332d10813ab789bg0191c4?chapterUid=50&rangeStart=4878&rangeEnd=4950"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046359_50_1399-1478",
      "chapterUid": 50,
      "range": "1399-1478",
      "markText": "当一只狗焦虑、愤怒、饥饿、迷惑、快乐或充满爱意时，它将这些情绪以最纯洁的形式呈现出来，我们也能感受得到，只不过人类的这些情感早被日益增长的复杂人性扭曲变形了。",
      "totalCount": 9826,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046359&chapterUid=50&rangeStart=1399&rangeEnd=1478",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/43332d10813ab789bg0191c4?chapterUid=50&rangeStart=1399&rangeEnd=1478"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046359_49_3339-3365",
      "chapterUid": 49,
      "range": "3339-3365",
      "markText": "“我对男人没有期待。唯有独处时，我才真正感到完整。”",
      "totalCount": 9306,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046359&chapterUid=49&rangeStart=3339&rangeEnd=3365",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/43332d10813ab789bg0191c4?chapterUid=49&rangeStart=3339&rangeEnd=3365"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046359_49_3828-3895",
      "chapterUid": 49,
      "range": "3828-3895",
      "markText": "她坦承自己的自私与懒惰，并说这两项或许是她人生的憾事，但她并不为此感到自责，“止于此就行了吧，因为天天看着不好的一面是相当无聊的事”。",
      "totalCount": 8347,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046359&chapterUid=49&rangeStart=3828&rangeEnd=3895",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/43332d10813ab789bg0191c4?chapterUid=49&rangeStart=3828&rangeEnd=3895"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046359_49_2145-2212",
      "chapterUid": 49,
      "range": "2145-2212",
      "markText": "虽然我有时会为自己在工作中的能力有限而感到羞愧，但我认为，个人生活比工作更重要，我并不为这个理念而感到羞愧——这是每个人都应该做的。”",
      "totalCount": 8333,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046359&chapterUid=49&rangeStart=2145&rangeEnd=2212",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/43332d10813ab789bg0191c4?chapterUid=49&rangeStart=2145&rangeEnd=2212"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046359_51_3054-3139",
      "chapterUid": 51,
      "range": "3054-3139",
      "markText": "这两人就是我浪漫主义阶段的最早受惠者，在这一阶段，爱情的形式是白日梦。我的激情对象常被我的幻想置于一些非常危险的境地，比如他家着火了，或者他被洪水冲走了，然后我去拯救他。",
      "totalCount": 8228,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046359&chapterUid=51&rangeStart=3054&rangeEnd=3139",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/43332d10813ab789bg0191c4?chapterUid=51&rangeStart=3054&rangeEnd=3139"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046359_50_1086-1161",
      "chapterUid": 50,
      "range": "1086-1161",
      "markText": "养狗最大的乐趣不就是和它一起到处溜达吗？看着它发现新路时兴高采烈，解开牵狗绳时欢欣雀跃，高兴地在草地上跳来蹦去，还不时开心地回头看看你是不是跟在后面。",
      "totalCount": 7974,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046359&chapterUid=50&rangeStart=1086&rangeEnd=1161",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/43332d10813ab789bg0191c4?chapterUid=50&rangeStart=1086&rangeEnd=1161"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046359_53_7229-7287",
      "chapterUid": 53,
      "range": "7229-7287",
      "markText": "我觉得在读者的意识深处，或随着他对文字内容的回应，所汲取的应该正好是自己需要、同时文字也正好能满足这一需要的部分吧。",
      "totalCount": 7514,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046359&chapterUid=53&rangeStart=7229&rangeEnd=7287",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/43332d10813ab789bg0191c4?chapterUid=53&rangeStart=7229&rangeEnd=7287"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046359_49_4140-4177",
      "chapterUid": 49,
      "range": "4140-4177",
      "markText": "年纪大了之后很少会在意外界的目光，更少会受尴尬困扰，这令她们感到更加自由。",
      "totalCount": 6832,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046359&chapterUid=49&rangeStart=4140&rangeEnd=4177",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/43332d10813ab789bg0191c4?chapterUid=49&rangeStart=4140&rangeEnd=4177"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046359_51_6132-6227",
      "chapterUid": 51,
      "range": "6132-6227",
      "markText": "这些无伤大雅的艳遇有些涉及别人的老公，但我从未心生愧疚，因为我从来没想过破坏别人的婚姻。如果我们的关系会被哪个老婆发现（实际上这种事情从未发生过），那也一定是因为她老公不小心，绝不会因为我。",
      "totalCount": 6539,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046359&chapterUid=51&rangeStart=6132&rangeEnd=6227",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/43332d10813ab789bg0191c4?chapterUid=51&rangeStart=6132&rangeEnd=6227"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046359_62_8881-8932",
      "chapterUid": 62,
      "range": "8881-8932",
      "markText": "我在很长一段时间都觉得自己生活得非常失败，但现在，当我回头看时，谁会相信啊，完全不是我当时想的那回事！",
      "totalCount": 6300,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046359&chapterUid=62&rangeStart=8881&rangeEnd=8932",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/43332d10813ab789bg0191c4?chapterUid=62&rangeStart=8881&rangeEnd=8932"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046359_54_3643-3687",
      "chapterUid": 54,
      "range": "3643-3687",
      "markText": "她不再具有调整自己去配合别人需求和口味的能力，你的作用无非是纵容她更多地沉浸于自我之中。",
